{"tid":161832,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做所有野都有心無力 好撚辛苦","createTime":"2017-03-18T19:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T02:25:07.000Z","uid":15020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e398b5862a34fa00d5a5552bf6264e09c84f48ef","tid":161832,"uid":15020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔知點解 呢排做咩野都好優柔寡斷<br />\n完全唔知自己做緊d咩野<br />\n<br />\n試過返學 本身已經落左車行緊去課室上堂 突然之間又唔想上 結果周圍行左陣又坐車返左屋企<br />\n<br />\n做功課溫書都係咁 明明已經諗住快d做結果都係拖到deadline先肯去做<br />\n<br />\n中同/fd聚會又決定唔到 一時又話去一時話唔去 loop左幾次搞到人地覺得我好似玩緊野咁<br />\n<br />\n連食飯都係 有時唔係太肚餓 落到街周圍行行左勁耐都諗唔到食咩 最後去返樓下求其買d野食 甚至唔食就咁返左屋企 我究竟係咪有病 唉"},{"pid":"b2b44efe8d8cb1dfbbb9ea3a6dddc1c1601dec5e","tid":161832,"uid":24220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:27:24.000Z","msg":"咁都叫有病？"},{"pid":"ccd8219ad529bdfc2feae738dea64e6ef0f87e45","tid":161832,"uid":15020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都叫有病？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知 可能本身個人廢掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d98656dc6f1d43786028b65d33015298f120ba","tid":161832,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:36:26.000Z","msg":"抑鬱?症狀有d似"},{"pid":"901232d143f10206e60c9148608db72bd4d3e9d1","tid":161832,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:40:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4be58dec1ef7c561f654299bde617b5a2ac06d6a","tid":161832,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4324d264d6d500d2650505024aea56f38b04a6e4","tid":161832,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:23:28.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n乜都唔想做 心情長期好down<br />\n開心唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多assessment 但係完全冇動力做<br />\n食野又係冇哂胃口 食少少就算<br />\n打機玩左一陣又放返低<br />\n唉 救命<img src=\"/as